   "updated": 1752700000000,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "a ~792-line while-loop in an EventStream\n\nwhile (tool calls or queued messages):\n    inject STEERING (you can talk mid-run)\n    stream one model turn\n    run tool calls (parallel by default)\n    emit events (turn_end, ...)\n\ncompaction: auto-summarize when\ncontext overflows",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "a ~792-line while-loop in an EventStream\n\nwhile (tool calls or queued messages):\n    inject STEERING (you can talk mid-run)\n    stream one model turn\n    run tool calls (parallel by default)\n    emit events (turn_end, ...)\n\ncompaction: auto-summarize when\ncontext overflows",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 14
  },
