  },
  {
   "id": "ext-body",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 970,
   "y": 255,
   "width": 315.70000000000005,
   "height": 309.40000000000003,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 2,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 284277890,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 906164397,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": [],
   "updated": 1752700000000,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "plain TypeScript files, hot-loaded (jiti)\n~/.pi/agent/extensions/*.ts or .pi/\n\n~30 lifecycle hooks:\n  input \u00b7 tool_call (can BLOCK) \u00b7\n  context \u00b7 session_compact \u00b7 ...\n\npi.registerTool / Command / Provider\n\n~70 examples shipped:\n  permission-gate (opt-in safety!)\n  plan mode \u00b7 subagents\n  git-checkpoint \u00b7 micro-VM sandbox\n  ...a playable DOOM overlay\n\n\"pi can create extensions.\n Ask it to build one.\"  \u2190 the thesis",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "plain TypeScript files, hot-loaded (jiti)\n~/.pi/agent/extensions/*.ts or .pi/\n\n~30 lifecycle hooks:\n  input \u00b7 tool_call (can BLOCK) \u00b7\n  context \u00b7 session_compact \u00b7 ...\n\npi.registerTool / Command / Provider\n\n~70 examples shipped:\n  permission-gate (opt-in safety!)\n  plan mode \u00b7 subagents\n  git-checkpoint \u00b7 micro-VM sandbox\n  ...a playable DOOM overlay\n\n\"pi can create extensions.\n Ask it to build one.\"  \u2190 the thesis",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 14
  },
